http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14333/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14333/canvas/1/af714afb-a94a-436c-bb94-6ded83e8a38d","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-07-03T00:00:20.370Z","creator":"ads","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Much of the plot and tensions in <em>Phantom Thread</em> revolve around how characters <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW207032574 BCX4\" href=\"https://digbmc.github.io/pt-annotated/items/phan-04258.html\"><u>view and watch</u></a> one another. Reynolds and Alma are constantly trying to read each other’s behaviors through glances and wordless communication. Reynolds uses his aesthetic vision to attempt to mold Alma into the woman he desires. The film’s haute couture context situates <em>Phantom Thread</em> in a world where everyone values and considers appearances.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14333/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:1362.3061803343949,291.5371218152866,228.56488853503174,262.711236066879"}}}]}]}]}